SOLAR, A Cozy Fireplace to enjoy during those cold nights, Large back yard that is your very own private oasis to enjoy, Tile countertops in the kitchen, and a NEWER HVAC system. Don't miss your opportunity to own this delightful home in Red Bluff! Schedule a showing today and experience the magic for yourself.
